          Whether you need shutters, blinds, or shades, we'll help you find the perfect solution for your home or business.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Shutters -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/shutter-1.jpg" alt="Plantation Shutters" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Plantation Shutters</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Timeless elegance meets modern functionality. Our plantation shutters are crafted from premium natural wood or durable composites, locally manufactured with a 25-year warranty.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1 mb-4">
              <li>‚úì Natural wood & composite options</li>
              <li>‚úì Custom sizes & shapes</li>
              <li>‚úì Energy efficient</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/services#shutters" class="text-primary-600 font-semibold hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
              Learn More
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Blinds -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/shutter-2.jpg" alt="Custom Blinds" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Custom Blinds</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              From vertical to horizontal, wood to aluminum ‚Äî we offer unlimited options to match your style and budget. Perfect light control for any room.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1 mb-4">
              <li>‚úì Wood, aluminum & fabric options</li>
              <li>‚úì Vertical & horizontal styles</li>
              <li>‚úì Budget-friendly choices</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/services#blinds" class="text-primary-600 font-semibold hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
              Learn More
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Shades -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition">
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/shutter-3.jpg" alt="Window Shades" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Window Shades</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Transform any space with simplicity. Our shades offer partial or complete light blocking, helping with energy efficiency, insulation, and privacy.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1 mb-4">
              <li>‚úì Room darkening options</li>
              <li>‚úì Energy efficient</li>
              <li>‚úì Modern & classic styles</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/services#shades" class="text-primary-600 font-semibold hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
              Learn More
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why St. Petersburg Homeowners Choose Us</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
            With over 35 years of experience in the construction field, we know window treatments inside and out. 
            We've worked from the Hamptons to New Jersey to St. Petersburg, bringing expertise and craftsmanship to every project.
          </p>
          
